  "audioSegments": [
    {
      "startTime": 0.11,
      "endTime": 3.03,
      "audioText": "为什么越自以为清醒的人越容易犯最愚蠢的错，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 3.13,
      "endTime": 5.01,
      "audioText": "这背后藏着最隐蔽的认知傲慢。"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 5.09,
      "endTime": 6.09,
      "audioText": "什么是认知傲慢，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 6.13,
      "endTime": 7.59,
      "audioText": "我用小猫给你解释一下，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 7.73,
      "endTime": 8.63,
      "audioText": "小猫从来不懂。"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 8.63,
      "endTime": 9.33,
      "audioText": "什么叫烦恼？"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 9.33,
      "endTime": 10.65,
      "audioText": "可社区里的其他小猫，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 10.71,
      "endTime": 11.91,
      "audioText": "日子从来都不轻松。"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 11.99,
      "endTime": 12.87,
      "audioText": "黑猫患了抑郁，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 12.95,
      "endTime": 14.01,
      "audioText": "整天耷拉着耳朵，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 14.01,
      "endTime": 14.91,
      "audioText": "趴在窝里不动。"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 14.99,
      "endTime": 16.39,
      "audioText": "小猫路过总笑着劝它，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 16.41,
      "endTime": 18.79,
      "audioText": "别总板着脸开心点蓝猫满是焦虑，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 18.79,
      "endTime": 19.51,
      "audioText": "整天魂不守，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 19.51,
      "endTime": 20.29,
      "audioText": "舍坐立不安。"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 20.31,
      "endTime": 22.81,
      "audioText": "它就说你就是想太多放宽心就没事。"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 22.93,
      "endTime": 23.95,
      "audioText": "橘猫严重社恐，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 24.03,
      "endTime": 25.39,
      "audioText": "每次聚会都躲在角落，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 25.41,
      "endTime": 26.11,
      "audioText": "浑身发抖，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 26.13,
      "endTime": 26.83,
      "audioText": "它又凑过去，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 26.83,
      "endTime": 27.79,
      "audioText": "喊你勇敢点，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 27.81,
      "endTime": 28.69,
      "audioText": "有什么好怕的，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 28.71,
      "endTime": 30.83,
      "audioText": "小猫一直不明白自己的好心安慰，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 30.85,
      "endTime": 32.03,
      "audioText": "为什么从来没人听？"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 32.11,
      "endTime": 33.59,
      "audioText": "小猫偶尔也会心情不好，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 33.61,
      "endTime": 34.67,
      "audioText": "但睡一觉就好了。"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 34.69,
      "endTime": 37.31,
      "audioText": "所以他以为黑猫的低落也能这样轻易缓解，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 37.35,
      "endTime": 38.39,
      "audioText": "他偶尔也会多想，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 38.45,
      "endTime": 40.19,
      "audioText": "但只要转移注意力就会没事。"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 40.27,
      "endTime": 41.69,
      "audioText": "所以它不懂蓝猫的焦虑，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 41.75,
      "endTime": 44.15,
      "audioText": "这就是心理学家说的虚假共识效应，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 44.23,
      "endTime": 45.21,
      "audioText": "就像小猫一样，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 45.27,
      "endTime": 47.91,
      "audioText": "总把自己的经验当成全世界的标准答案。"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 47.99,
      "endTime": 50.79,
      "audioText": "可为什么小猫始终无法理解其他猫的难呢？"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 50.85,
      "endTime": 52.71,
      "audioText": "这背后都是认知吝啬在作怪，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 52.83,
      "endTime": 54.15,
      "audioText": "就像原始时代的小猫，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 54.17,
      "endTime": 55.53,
      "audioText": "看到黑影就立刻逃跑，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 55.61,
      "endTime": 56.13,
      "audioText": "不用细究，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 56.13,
      "endTime": 57.03,
      "audioText": "那是不是野兽？"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 57.09,
      "endTime": 58.37,
      "audioText": "这是大脑为了节省力气，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 58.37,
      "endTime": 59.935,
      "audioText": "会刻意剔除琐碎信息，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 60.2,
      "endTime": 62.26,
      "audioText": "只用自己熟悉的经验去判断事情。"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 62.34,
      "endTime": 63.76,
      "audioText": "小猫的大脑也是这样，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 63.78,
      "endTime": 65.62,
      "audioText": "它懒得去深究黑猫的低落，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 65.62,
      "endTime": 67.3,
      "audioText": "蓝猫的心慌到底是为什么？"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 67.3,
      "endTime": 68.68,
      "audioText": "他也懒得去了解橘猫，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 68.68,
      "endTime": 70.64,
      "audioText": "躲在沙发底时心里有多害怕，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 70.72,
      "endTime": 73.16,
      "audioText": "它只用自己的日常经验轻易下了判断，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 73.24,
      "endTime": 74.3,
      "audioText": "这就是认知傲慢。"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 74.32,
      "endTime": 75.08,
      "audioText": "他不懂痛苦，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 75.08,
      "endTime": 76.1,
      "audioText": "是私人定制的秤，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 76.159,
      "endTime": 77.58,
      "audioText": "每个人的砝码都不通用，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 77.7,
      "endTime": 79.14,
      "audioText": "如同落在你头上的导弹，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 79.22,
      "endTime": 80.64,
      "audioText": "不过是别人眼中的流星，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 80.78,
      "endTime": 82.62,
      "audioText": "你的解药未必是别人的良方。"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 82.68,
      "endTime": 84.28,
      "audioText": "我们都习惯了用自己的认知，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 84.36,
      "endTime": 85.54,
      "audioText": "去定义别人的困境，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 85.68,
      "endTime": 86.28,
      "audioText": "认知傲慢，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 86.28,
      "endTime": 87.16,
      "audioText": "从来都不是坏，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 87.24,
      "endTime": 88.48,
      "audioText": "而是我们的大脑太懒，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 88.56,
      "endTime": 89.8,
      "audioText": "懒到不愿放下自己的。"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 89.8,
      "endTime": 91.205,
      "audioText": "我以为去承认我不懂。"
    }
  ],
